# thumbnailDictionaryKey

**Type Property**

A dictionary of NSImage/UIImage objects keyed by size (read-write). See [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLThumbnailDictionaryItem] for a list of possible keys.

## Declaration

```swift
static let thumbnailDictionaryKey: URLResourceKey
```

## Thumbnail keys

- **thumbnailKey**: All thumbnails as a single NSImage (read-write).
- **URLThumbnailDictionaryItem**: Possible keys for the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLResourceKey/thumbnailDictionaryKey] dictionary.
